name: The Gaze
description:
It is present. As long as you are.
The sinister look that you always felt on your back, now spreads throughout your room. It gazes you. As long as you gaze.
It is waiting for the right moment.

This is a special mint. The purpose of The Gaze is not to be collected, but to be passed to as much people as it's possible. To gaze and be gazed. To be cursed and curse.
Let it spread as a disease that can't be cured.
